list.content:
拿最近一次的项目Email为例子
改动前
My duties of the tournament
Design the questionaire for tournament feedback collection；
Manage Registration payment(Company Alipay)：Check and feedback every payment during the registration； 
Purchase tournament supplies which include: Tee/Tee marker/flag/towel/unbrella/skin coat for outsourses team/tent/badage；
Purhase Office and players' supplies；
Hotel arrangement for committee and part of paid clients and potencial clients;
Transportation for picking up and drop off the airport for committee/players/coach;
Manage the catering for committee;
Shuttle car from hotel to club house;
Manage the cashflow and payment to outsource team;
Manage the invoices from all parties;
Manage the award ceremony;
Packing with the team and clean up.

改动后
Before the tournament（赛前）
Design the questionaire for tournament feedback collection；
Manage Registration payment(Company Alipay)：Check and feedback every payment during the registration； 
Purchase tournament supplies which include: Tee/Tee marker/flag/towel/unbrella/skin coat for outsourses team/tent/badage；
Purhase Office and players' supplies；
Hotel arrangement for committee and part of paid clients and potencial clients;
Transportation for picking up and drop off the airport for committee/players/coach;

During the tournament（赛中）
Manage the catering for committee;
Shuttle car from hotel to club house;
Manage the award ceremony;

After the Tournament（赛后）
Manage the cashflow and payment to outsource team;
Manage the invoices from all parties;
Packing with the team and clean up.
